<li id="cite_note-25"><b><a href="#cite_ref-25" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFMills1981">Mills, A. A., (August 1981). "<a href="http://www.jstor.org/view/00359149/ap020059/02a00030/0?frame=noframe&amp;userID=836f0866@cam.ac.uk/01cc99332500501b52b38&amp;dpi=3&amp;config=jstor" class="external text" title="http://www.jstor.org/view/00359149/ap020059/02a00030/0?frame=noframe&amp;userID=836f0866@cam.ac.uk/01cc99332500501b52b38&amp;dpi=3&amp;config=jstor" rel="nofollow">Roger Bacon's Theory of the Rainbow: Progress or Regress?</a>" (<sup class="noprint Inline-Template"><span title="&#160;since May 2008" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Dead_external_links" title="Wikipedia:Dead external links">dead link</a></i>]</span></sup>). <i>Notes and Records of the Royal Society of London</i> <b>36</b> (1): 13–36. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1098%2Frsnr.1981.0002" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1098%2Frsnr.1981.0002" rel="nofollow">10.1098/rsnr.1981.0002</a></span><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.jstor.org/view/00359149/ap020059/02a00030/0?frame=noframe&amp;userID=836f0866@cam.ac.uk/01cc99332500501b52b38&amp;dpi=3&amp;config=jstor" class="external free" title="http://www.jstor.org/view/00359149/ap020059/02a00030/0?frame=noframe&amp;userID=836f0866@cam.ac.uk/01cc99332500501b52b38&amp;dpi=3&amp;config=jstor" rel="nofollow">http://www.jstor.org/view/00359149/ap020059/02a00030/0?frame=noframe&amp;userID=836f0866@cam.ac.uk/01cc99332500501b52b38&amp;dpi=3&amp;config=jstor</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-06-07</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Roger+Bacon%27s+Theory+of+the+Rainbow%3A+Progress+or+Regress%3F&amp;rft.jtitle=Notes+and+Re